</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A Van Nuys man serving a five-month sentence for drunk driving remained at 
large Sunday after escaping from the Peter Pitchess Honor Rancho a day earlier, 
Los Angeles County sheriff's deputies said. 
</P>
<P>
 Max Arroyo, 27, was last seen at 3 a.m. Saturday in a minimum-security ward of 
