<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 18, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Special Section; Part W; Page 11; Column 1; Sports Desk 
</P>
